Fix of the candidate-list in using ibus-pinyin is out of order

the problem is caused by the new version of libsqlite

For not be mixed up the original Ubuntu system ( lots of tool are using libsqlite as well)
create a script as the snippet code to preload an older version of libsqlite
check install.sh about the detailed

sqlite_3.22/ is the pre-build binary of libsqlite, and verified on 20.04, 22.04
may need to re-build in future distro
